<L>__{exterior rural roads later that night}
<A>__{landon speeds, the windows open, wind whipping, dire straits blasting. the camaro turns and brakes and turns again, kicking up gravel, raising hell. the car slides to a stop.}
<L>__{interior camaro}
<A>__{landon turns off the radio. sits still. wipes the rearview mirror clean, spotless. unties the dangling plastic skeleton and pockets it.}
<L>__{exterior used car lot next morning}
